><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 818 262 1073 309"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1083 267 1149 303"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1158 265 1233 303"></span>holter Übung behereſ&lt;t, Dementſprechend ift die Prüfungsarbeit aus dem</span><span class="ocr_line" title="bbox 12 327 1232 377"><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 12 329 226 377"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 236 334 294 371"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 300 332 437 377"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 445 338 487 377"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 493 332 678 377"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 688 328 751 370"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 756 331 818 377"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 823 328 905 377"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 908 341 951 376"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 956 327 1158 376"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1165 332 1232 370"></span>Arbeitsgebiet des Berufes zu entnehmen. Sie ſoll nicht zu umfangreich und</span><span class="ocr_line" title="bbox 12 389 1234 446"><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 12 397 94 445"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 100 406 143 445"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 148 396 291 445"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 296 401 375 446"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 384 400 484 440"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 493 401 532 440"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 539 402 595 440"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 602 406 659 445"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 666 399 848 446"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 857 389 1009 444"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1018 397 1156 444"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1163 399 1234 438"></span>nicht zu vielteilig ſein, Hamit in der zur Verfügung ſtehenden Prüfzeit eine</span><span class="ocr_line" title="bbox 14 464 852 514"><span class="ocrx_word" title="